um devices.","Bose views sound as an investment and encourages you to do the same. Though its prices might seem daunting, if you spend a lot of time outside and value the best sound, then Bose is a good choice for you. If a complete Bose sound system is not an option for you, then Bose offers other outdoor solutions. Its wireless outdoor speakers are small and portable, yet they can transmit audio over a substantial area. Furthermore, these small speakers can play for up to eight hours on one charge, so you do not have to worry about the party being cut short when the speakers die.","Bose offers the best line of outdoor speakers with unmatched sound and quality devices. Any outdoor device from this brand is the best choice if you want a luxury brand for your outdoor sound system."]},"id":"95d5f20f-ff83-4f3d-8561-4b7751aa0c9a","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/vekPFyGWEX23Stiar4UJj.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"https://www.toptenreviews.comhttp://cdn.toptenreviews.com/rev/prod/large/68918-bose-box.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vekPFyGWEX23Stiar4UJj.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"vekPFyGWEX23Stiar4UJj","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vekPFyGWEX23Stiar4UJj.jpg","alt":""},"id":"ce3846ab-be92-43ba-9c3b-ce0df3791ffb","type":"image"},{"data":{"hawk":"{\"data-model-name\":\"Bose\", \"data-widget-type\":\"price\"}","linkText":"Visit Site","url":"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0001H9TGI/?&tag=ttr_outdoor_speaker-20&ascsubtag=[site|ttr[cat|630[art|NA[pid|68918[tid|NA[bbc|NA","specs":null,"subtitle":"","urlStyle":"button","review":{"rating":0,"url":"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/best-outdoor-speakers,review-2785.html","name":"Bose","id":""},"noFollow":false,"title":"<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/best-outdoor-speakers,review-2785.html\">Bose</a>","pros":["Empty List"],"cons":["Empty List"]},"id":"994e51f6-6f12-48e2-a37e-ec2fc8d99d51","type":"buying-guide"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["